<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 18:09:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>停火。预防加沙和以色列婴儿脊髓灰质炎流行的唯一方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/cease-fire-the-only-way-to-prevent-polio-epidemic-among-gazan-and-israeli-babies/00000190-d57e-dbe5-a7fa-f77eb5030000</link><description>最近在加沙污水中发现的高传染性脊髓灰质炎病毒的威胁，必须协调和全面地应对。作为以色列公共卫生教授，我们呼吁停火以阻止疫情蔓延</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 17:11:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/cease-fire-the-only-way-to-prevent-polio-epidemic-among-gazan-and-israeli-babies/00000190-d57e-dbe5-a7fa-f77eb5030000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 289 天：以色列称在以色列国防军袭击也门后拦截了胡塞武装导弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-289-israel-says-it-intercepted-houthi-missile-after-idfs-yemen-strike/00000190-d636-dc1d-a5d1-f73f0f2b0000</link><description>以色列荷台达袭击后，胡塞武装称他们向以色列南部埃拉特发射导弹，袭击了红海的美国船只 ■ 以色列称其用“箭 3”防御系统拦截了胡塞武装导弹，中央司令部称其击落了胡塞武装无人机 ■ 犹太定居者袭击巴勒斯坦和以色列团体约旦河西岸的活动分子造成数人受伤 ■ 内塔尼亚胡将于周二会见拜登 ■ 战争进入 289 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 17:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-289-israel-says-it-intercepted-houthi-missile-after-idfs-yemen-strike/00000190-d636-dc1d-a5d1-f73f0f2b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将就国际法院裁决将如何影响加沙援助向最高法院提供补充论据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-give-top-court-supplementary-arguments-on-how-icj-ruling-will-affect-gaza-aid/00000190-d5dd-dac7-a1f8-ddddba5e0000</link><description>法官们正在听取人权组织的请愿书，呼吁增加对加沙的人道主义援助。他们的裁决将影响国家对加沙的责任，国际法院称以色列仍然是占领军</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 16:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-give-top-court-supplementary-arguments-on-how-icj-ruling-will-affect-gaza-aid/00000190-d5dd-dac7-a1f8-ddddba5e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对也门的袭击：战术上的成功暴露了战略上的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-strike-on-yemen-a-tactical-success-that-exposes-a-strategic-failure/00000190-d5c1-dd26-af91-ffffbbe30000</link><description>以色列飞行员飞那么远去轰炸也门的一个港口，这证明了其对伊朗这个真正的、更近的威胁的威慑力是多么有限。责任归咎于总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡，他对伊朗核威胁的痴迷意味着他忽视了其代理人的危险</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 16:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-strike-on-yemen-a-tactical-success-that-exposes-a-strategic-failure/00000190-d5c1-dd26-af91-ffffbbe30000</guid></item><item><title>三名民主党人如何为内塔尼亚胡在华盛顿的“全面胜利”铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-21/ty-article/.highlight/how-three-democrats-paved-the-way-for-netanyahus-total-victory-in-washington/00000190-d5c5-d548-a3ba-ffcfbc830000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡本周将庆祝的将是个人和政治上的胜利：10 月 7 日的灾难将永远玷污他的遗产，十个月后，他将在美国之行期间获得新的公众合法性感</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 16:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-21/ty-article/.highlight/how-three-democrats-paved-the-way-for-netanyahus-total-victory-in-washington/00000190-d5c5-d548-a3ba-ffcfbc830000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在未咨询总检察长的情况下提交内阁决定，拒绝国际法院的咨询意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-files-draft-decision-that-rejects-icjs-advisory-opinion-without-consulting-ag/00000190-d544-d65c-a390-fdd598650000</link><description>以色列拒绝国际法院在内塔尼亚胡提交的裁决草案中发表的咨询意见。 “以色列人民不是自己土地和永恒首都耶路撒冷的占领者”</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 13:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-files-draft-decision-that-rejects-icjs-advisory-opinion-without-consulting-ag/00000190-d544-d65c-a390-fdd598650000</guid></item><item><title>咨询委员会要求以色列总检察长提供有关本格维尔任命的警察局长腐败指控的详细信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/committee-asks-israels-ag-for-details-on-ben-gvir-picked-police-chiefs-violations/00000190-d4fb-d89a-a1f7-f6fb7b310000</link><description>咨询委员会将于周日就佩莱德的候选资格举行第二次会议，预计将在未来几天内敲定其立场。以色列总检察长尚未就佩莱德的任命给出最终意见，但此前曾表示，委员们应该拥有无瑕疵的记录</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 13:54:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/committee-asks-israels-ag-for-details-on-ben-gvir-picked-police-chiefs-violations/00000190-d4fb-d89a-a1f7-f6fb7b310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对胡塞武装的袭击：合理吗？是的。比例？不，游戏规则改变者？不太可能</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-attack-on-the-houthis-justified-yes-proportionate-no-game-changer-unlikely/00000190-d52f-d89a-a1f7-f7af04990000</link><description>沙特阿拉伯和阿联酋已经与胡塞武装作战了八年。加沙战争爆发以来，美英已数十次袭击胡塞武装目标。认为以色列的一次袭击就能改变矩阵的想法是错误的。避免多战区冲突的唯一方法是在加沙达成人质和停火协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 13:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-attack-on-the-houthis-justified-yes-proportionate-no-game-changer-unlikely/00000190-d52f-d89a-a1f7-f7af04990000</guid></item><item><title>弱点：看不到巴勒斯坦人，以色列人就不再看到自己</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-blind-side-not-seeing-the-palestinians-is-not-seeing-ourselves/00000190-d4a6-dd02-a3d3-ffff5e5d0000</link><description>根据当今以色列普遍的情绪，谈论我们在加沙真正所做的事情比在那里实施的实际行为更糟糕</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-blind-side-not-seeing-the-palestinians-is-not-seeing-ourselves/00000190-d4a6-dd02-a3d3-ffff5e5d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙污水中发现高浓度病毒后，以色列国防军将为以色列士兵接种脊髓灰质炎疫苗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-to-vaccinate-israeli-soldiers-after-polio-found-in-gaza-sewage/00000190-d490-decf-a7b2-d5b797d50000</link><description>根据以色列军队掌握的信息，以色列军队表示，尚未确认加沙有任何临床病例，但确实担心可能爆发脊髓灰质炎，特别是考虑到加沙的情况</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-to-vaccinate-israeli-soldiers-after-polio-found-in-gaza-sewage/00000190-d490-decf-a7b2-d5b797d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列担心国际法院的裁决将导致国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特发出逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-icj-opinion-will-lead-to-icc-arrest-warrants-for-netanyahu-and-gallant/00000190-d473-dd02-a3d3-ffff9b5a0000</link><description>尽管与国际刑事法院发出国际刑事逮捕令没有直接关系，但法官们将无法忽视国际法院关于以色列违反国际法的咨询意见</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:17:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-icj-opinion-will-lead-to-icc-arrest-warrants-for-netanyahu-and-gallant/00000190-d473-dd02-a3d3-ffff9b5a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡“红线”推迟与哈马斯的人质交易，满怀希望的布林肯等待以色列总理的“第二天”计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-red-lines-delay-hostage-deal-as-hopeful-blinken-awaits-pms-day-after-plan/00000190-d420-decf-a7b2-d5b751680000</link><description>在总理预计访问华盛顿并向国会发表讲话之前，内塔尼亚胡和以色列谈判团队就人质协议仍存在分歧</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 08:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-red-lines-delay-hostage-deal-as-hopeful-blinken-awaits-pms-day-after-plan/00000190-d420-decf-a7b2-d5b751680000</guid></item><item><title>美国：国际法院对约旦河西岸占领的意见可能会使冲突的解决变得复杂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-icj-opinion-on-west-bank-occupation-could-complicate-resolving-the-conflict/00000190-d3dd-dd02-a3d3-fbdfb0220000</link><description>美国国务院补充说，法院的意见与解决冲突的“既定框架不一致”，华盛顿“强烈反对”各方利用法院的意见“作为进一步单方面行动的借口”</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 06:38:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-icj-opinion-on-west-bank-occupation-could-complicate-resolving-the-conflict/00000190-d3dd-dd02-a3d3-fbdfb0220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党跨境贸易猛烈；以色列国防军称两名士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-blows-across-border-idf-says-two-soldiers-injured/00000190-d303-dbb4-a7d2-db0f14160000</link><description>以色列军方表示，有 40 枚火箭弹和无人机越过边境发射，造成两名士兵受伤并引发火灾。黎巴嫩报道称，以色列国防军袭击了真主党军火库和一辆车辆，造成至少四名平民受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 02:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-blows-across-border-idf-says-two-soldiers-injured/00000190-d303-dbb4-a7d2-db0f14160000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德负责人率领的以色列代表团周四启程前往卡塔尔参加人质谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article-live/fires-rage-in-northern-israel-after-rocket-fire-sources-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000190-d2bb-dd40-ab95-f6bbc5be0000</link><description>以色列袭击也门胡塞武装港口，胡塞武装称 6 人死亡、87 人受伤 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部称，在过去 24 小时内，有 64 名巴勒斯坦人在以色列国防军的袭击中丧生 ■ 辛贝特逮捕了约旦河西岸大学的学生，怀疑他们策划了一次恐怖袭击哈马斯 ■ 以色列国防军表示，大约有 10 枚火箭弹在上加利利发射，导致该地区起火；达夫纳基布兹高中和其他建筑受损</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 00:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article-live/fires-rage-in-northern-israel-after-rocket-fire-sources-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000190-d2bb-dd40-ab95-f6bbc5be0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院关于以色列占领的裁决的执行取决于联合国和美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/implementation-of-icj-ruling-on-israeli-occupation-depends-on-the-un-and-u-s/00000190-d1d0-dd40-ab95-f7dbe2710000</link><description>国际法院正式表示，以色列对约旦河西岸的占领是“非法的”，必须予以拆除。这项裁决虽然不具有约束力，但却给以色列带来了压力，并可能改变现实，但以色列的盟友和国际社会需要认真对待它</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 00:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/implementation-of-icj-ruling-on-israeli-occupation-depends-on-the-un-and-u-s/00000190-d1d0-dd40-ab95-f7dbe2710000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列对也门的首次袭击，战争在九个月后出现了危险的新转折</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/with-israels-first-ever-attack-in-yemen-the-war-takes-a-dangerous-new-turn/00000190-d1ce-dd02-a3d3-fbdff1850000</link><description>这次袭击的成功——距离以色列约 1,700 公里——向整个地区，特别是伊朗传达了以色列远程军事能力的信息。这次袭击以及周末的其他新闻给内塔尼亚胡总理本已颇具争议的美国之行带来了更多负担</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 22:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/with-israels-first-ever-attack-in-yemen-the-war-takes-a-dangerous-new-turn/00000190-d1ce-dd02-a3d3-fbdff1850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在特拉维夫无人机致命袭击后袭击也门；胡塞武装誓言做出回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/israel-attacks-yemen-following-fatal-tel-aviv-drone-strike-houthis-vow-to-respond/00000190-d10d-d5cb-a59c-fd4f1ea80000</link><description>胡塞武装报告称，周五的袭击造成 6 人死亡、87 人受伤，炼油厂和电力基础设施受损。周六，以色列国防军拦截了一枚从也门向以色列南部埃拉特发射的地对地导弹</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 20:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/israel-attacks-yemen-following-fatal-tel-aviv-drone-strike-houthis-vow-to-respond/00000190-d10d-d5cb-a59c-fd4f1ea80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 288 天：以色列国防军袭击也门；黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 40 枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-288-israel-strikes-in-yemen-40-rockets-from-lebanon-launched-at-north/00000190-d156-dc8b-a1dd-d9f70c890000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，在胡塞武装无人机袭击特拉维夫一天后，以色列袭击了也门胡塞武装控制的荷台达港，造成一人死亡 ■ 黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 40 多枚火箭弹 ■ 据报道，至少 30 人死亡以色列袭击加沙拉法 ■ 《纽约时报》报道，拜登不会在总理内塔尼亚胡下周访问华盛顿之前退出总统竞选</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 18:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-288-israel-strikes-in-yemen-40-rockets-from-lebanon-launched-at-north/00000190-d156-dc8b-a1dd-d9f70c890000</guid></item><item><title>随着内塔尼亚胡前往美国，以色列人开始了为期一周的人质协议和反对政府的抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-open-week-of-protests-for-hostage-deal-against-govt-as-netanyahu-heads-to-u-s/00000190-d058-dbb4-a7d2-db5f671e0000</link><description>周六，以色列各地数十个地点发生了示威活动，有报道称谈判取得了进展。未来一周，人质亲属计划跟随内塔尼亚胡总理访问美国，并在他计划向国会发表讲话期间举行大规模集会</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 15:01:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-open-week-of-protests-for-hostage-deal-against-govt-as-netanyahu-heads-to-u-s/00000190-d058-dbb4-a7d2-db5f671e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>